475ba6e53bc3062aeaf4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/insta360s-latest-tiny-action-cam-comes-with-a-wireless-display-130001905.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/insta360s-latest-tiny-action-cam-comes-with-a-wireless-display-130001905.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9cfc0a18-dd8f-4dc6-b4dc-b7fc76a961fa</guid><dc:creator> Richard Lai</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 13:00:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687871659</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T13:14:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Richard Lai]]></category><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/2c1f7730-14e5-11ee-b677-5734a388a08b" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/2c1f7730-14e5-11ee-b677-5734a388a08b" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Insta360]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Insta360 Go 3 with its thumb-sized camera detached from its 'Action Pod' body for remote viewing.]]></media